OL,3,CWRU set to announce plans to cut
OL,4,Cnumber of pro clubs in Wales from four
OL,5,Cto two
OL,7,FThe Welsh Rugby Union is expected to
OL,8,Fannounce its plans to cut the number
OL,9,Fof professional clubs in Wales from
OL,10,Ffour to two.
OL,12,FWelsh rugby's governing body is
OL,13,Fexpected to officially lay out its
OL,14,Fplans for the future of the game over
OL,15,Fthe coming days.
OL,17,FIf approved, it would mark a seismic
OL,18,Fchange to the professional game in
OL,19,FWales.
