OL,3,CWRU set to announce plans to cut
OL,4,Cnumber of pro clubs in Wales from four
OL,5,Cto two
OL,7,FA formal consultation process is
OL,8,Fexpected to begin this week, where the
OL,9,FWRU will enter discussions with the
OL,10,Ffour existing professional clubs -
OL,11,FCardiff, Dragons, Ospreys and Scarlets
OL,12,F- along with the supporter groups of
OL,13,Feach club, a panel of fans, and the
OL,14,FWelsh Rugby Players Association.
OL,16,FIt is not clear whether the two
OL,17,Fsurviving clubs would be any of the
OL,18,Fexisting four, who will all be
OL,19,Freadying themselves for a fight for
OL,20,Fsurvival.
