OL,3,CWRU set to announce plans to cut
OL,4,Cnumber of pro clubs in Wales from four
OL,5,Cto two
OL,7,FWhat is brewing is set to eclipse the
OL,8,Fabandoned merger between the Ospreys
OL,9,Fand Scarlets in 2019 and the threat of
OL,10,Fstrike action on the eve of Wales'
OL,11,F2023 clash with England.
OL,13,FBack in May, the WRU abandoned its
OL,14,Fintention to continue funding four
OL,15,Fprofessional clubs evenly: the
OL,16,Fcollapse of Cardiff and then its
OL,17,Ftakeover by the WRU, declining
OL,18,Fbroadcast revenues and the financial
OL,19,Fimpact of Wales' historic 18-match
OL,20,Flosing run being worse than projected
OL,21,Fhave been cited as some of the reasons.
