OL,3,CWRU set to announce plans to cut
OL,4,Cnumber of pro clubs in Wales from four
OL,5,Cto two
OL,7,FIt followed the Union and four clubs
OL,8,Ffailing to settle on a new equal
OL,9,Ffunding model.
OL,11,FEach side will argue it should be
OL,12,Famong those to stay.
OL,14,FCardiff are now owned by the WRU
OL,15,Ffollowing the club's collapse in
OL,16,FApril, while the Ospreys are ploughing
OL,17,Fahead with a planned redevelopment of
OL,18,Fthe historic St Helen's ground in
OL,19,FSwansea which would see the club have
OL,20,Fits own ground after previously using
OL,21,Fthe Swansea.com Stadium.
