OL,3,CWRU set to announce plans to cut
OL,4,Cnumber of pro clubs in Wales from four
OL,5,Cto two
OL,7,FThe Scarlets only this month announced
OL,8,Fsignificant investment from US company
OL,9,FHouse of Luxury, whose sports
OL,10,Fdepartment is led by former WRU CEO
OL,11,FDavid Moffett. The Kiwi was at the
OL,12,Fhelm of Welsh rugby when the regions
OL,13,Fwere created in 2003 and has often
OL,14,Fdivided opinions. On HOL's Sports
OL,15,FAdvisory Board is former Wales fly-
OL,16,Fhalf and Ospreys legend Dan Biggar.
