OL,3,CWRU set to announce plans to cut
OL,4,Cnumber of pro clubs in Wales from four
OL,5,Cto two
OL,7,FThe Dragons have issued a statement
OL,8,Fthis week, saying its ambition to
OL,9,Fbuild a club "that could thrive both
OL,10,Fon and off the field" has not changed,
OL,11,Fadding: "Elite rugby must remain in
OL,12,FGwent and Dragons RFC has every reason
OL,13,Fto continue proudly in its current
OL,14,Fform."
OL,16,FBy October, the WRU anticipates it
OL,17,Fwill have a decision on how Welsh
OL,18,Frugby will proceed.
